reviews.review_text: broken bottle i have a lot to say about this particular night,but for now ill just tell you ,listen close,at 3;38-3;40 in Comes A Time you can hear the bottle smash on billy's snare.i found it years ago on my tape.this was a high energy night,with a punchy sound,and a post G.D.T.R.F.B. jam i like.but oh man that damn bottle!i know,i was there
